actions.message:
**"/info"** - Minim de Informatii ale server-ului !
**"/warn"** - Ofera 1/3 warn unui user !
**"/warn-2"** - Ofera 2/3 warn unui user !
**"/dwarn"** - Ofera DiscordWarn 1/3 unui user !
**"/dwarn-2"** - Ofera DiscordWarn 2/3 unui user !
**"/fwarn"** - Ofera FactionWarn 1/3 unui user !
**"/fwarn-2"** - Ofera FactionWarn 2/3 unui user !
**"/staffwarn"** - Ofera StaffWarn 1/3 unui user !
**"/staffwarn-2"** - Ofera StaffWarn 2/3 unui user !
**"/ban"** - Cand user-ul face 3/3 warn's i se va oferi aceasta comanda , care da gradul de BANNED pe discord !
